		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- Using <a href="http://nesdev.com/s0.zip" class="postlink">this demo</a>, I noticed an annoyance (in my emu) regarding sprite zero hits. Let's assume a (solid) square:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">****<br />*..*<br />*..*<br />*..*<br />****</div>
<br />
<br />- When the sprite is over the * region of the square, the black bar flickers. Any special reason for this???

		

		</td>
